<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: #fff;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .main-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2a2a8f;
            text-align: center;
            margin: 10px 0 5px;
        }

        .sub-title {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #4a4a4a;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .content {
            line-height: 1.6;
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .content .highlight {
            color: #2a2a8f;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .cta {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .cta button {
            background-color: #2a2a8f;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            font-size: 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .cta button:hover {
            background-color: #1f1f6f;
        }

        .contact-options {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .contact-button {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #2a2a8f;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            border: 2px solid #2a2a8f;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .contact-button img {
            width: 20px;
        }

        .booking-info {
            margin: 40px 0;
        }

        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .info-item {
            background: #f1f3f5;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .info-item strong {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .booking-summary {
            margin-top: 30px;
            background: #f1f3f5;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .flight-details {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }

        .flight-details:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .airline-logo img {
            max-width: 60px;
        }

        .flight-info {
            flex: 1;
            margin-left: 15px;
        }

        .flight-info p {
            margin: 5px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .note {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
            margin-top: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .note .highlight {
            color: #2a2a8f;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #333;
        }

        /* Responsive Design */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .info-grid {
                grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .contact-button {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                padding: 10px;
            }

            .flight-details {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
                gap: 10px;
            }

            .flight-info {
                margin-left: 0;
                text-align: center;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 480px) {
            .info-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .cta button {
                width: 100%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="main-title">Your Booking is Confirmed</h1>
        <p class="sub-title">Finish Payment to Secure Your Ticket</p>

        <p class="content">Dear <span class="highlight">Saleh Ahmed</span>,</p>
        <p class="content">
            Thank you for booking with Flyit Search! We're excited to assist you with your travel plans.
            <br><br>
            To secure your booking and receive your ticket, <span class="highlight">please complete the payment within the next 20 minutes.</span>
            Flight fares are subject to change, so we recommend prompt payment to lock in your current rate.
            <br><br>
            Once your payment is successful, your ticket will be issued and sent directly to your email.
        </p>
        <p class="content">Safe travels with Flyit Search!</p>

        <div class="cta">
            <button>Confirm Booking</button>
            <div class="contact-options">
                <a href="tel:01736-987906" class="contact-button">
                    <img src="phone-icon.png" alt="Phone Icon"> Call for Assistance
                </a>
                <a href="#" class="contact-button">
                    <img src="message-icon.png" alt="Message Icon"> Send Message
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="booking-info">
            <h2>Booking Information:</h2>
            <div class="info-grid">
                <div class="info-item">
                    <strong>Booking ID</strong>
                    FIS7520037928887
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <strong>Traveler's Name</strong>
                    MR HASIBUL ISLAM
                </div>
                <div class="info-item">
                    <strong>Type</strong>
                    Adult
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="booking-summary">
            <h2>Booking Summary</h2>
            <!-- Flight details go here -->
        </div>

        <p class="note">
            Please note that <span class="highlight">this is a provisional flight booking</span> and is not a confirmed ticket or final confirmation of your travel plans. This booking may be subject to cancellation at any time.
        </p>
        <footer>
            <p>Thank you, <br> Team Flyit Search</p>
        </footer>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
